# A. VeraCrypt support in GNOME

## A.4 Add VeraCrypt support to udisks

We worked with upstream on the libblockdev and udisks changes (pull requests [#320](https://github.com/storaged-project/libblockdev/pull/320) and [#495](https://github.com/storaged-project/udisks/pull/495)). The libblockdev pull request was successfully merged ([[!tails_ticket 15219]]).

## A.6 Add VeraCrypt support to GNOME Files

We worked on supporting VeraCrypt volumes in the unlock dialog opened by gvfs-udisks2-volume-monitor, which allows unlocking encrypted volumes via GNOME Files, or when the storage device is plugged in ([[!tails_ticket 15218]]).

